Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity

Class ExternalOperatorDescription

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity.ExternalOperatorDescription
public class ExternalOperatorDescription extends Object
Represents the description of an external operator.
An external operator defines an operation that is applied in a workflow or processing pipeline, detailing the types and numbers of operands it requires, and a description of its function.
